CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, October 10, 1953, pg. 21 reads: "They'll Be Living Here - These are some of the families which have purchased homes in Belmar Gardens. First occupancy is expected early next spring."
TitMainTitle: Crowd of men, women, and children, including girl wearing dress with striped bodice, gathered on site of Belmar Gardens for groundbreaking, with light colored tent, American flag, and trees
